definitions.definition: Resembling or worthy of a picture or painting ; having the qualities of a picture or painting; pleasingly beautiful.
examples: We looked down onto a beautiful, picturesque sunset over the ocean.

definitions.definition: Strikingly graphic or vivid ; having striking and vivid imagery .

main_definition: Resembling or worthy of a picture or painting ; having the qualities of a picture or painting; pleasingly beautiful.
secondary_definitions: ( figurative , by extension ) Strikingly graphic or vivid ; having striking and vivid imagery .
